net.minecraftforge.fluids.capability.templates

类 VoidFluidHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.fluids.capability.templates.VoidFluidHandler
  • 所有已实现的接口:

    直接已知子类:
    BlockWrapper

    public class VoidFluidHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFluidHandler, IFluidTank
    VoidFluidHandler is a template fluid handler that can be filled indefinitely without ever getting full. It does not store fluid that gets filled into it, but "destroys" it upon receiving it.
